              I spend a good chunk of time writing Excel macros and I was curious to see his handy work. Unlocking his macros wasn't that difficult and there's guides all over the internet on how to do this.<br /><br />I would publish the unlocked version if he hadn't explicitly said he didn't want it released, but if you really want to take a look at it, it's not that difficult to do yourself.

              

              
              
